      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> creamed</strong> <strong>coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>",
