    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the curry is cooking, finely dice the <strong>tomatoes</strong></p><p>Chop most of the<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks (reserve a few leaves for garnish)</p><p>Combine the <strong>diced tomatoes </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato & coriander salad</strong></p>",
