      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then chop it roughly</p><p>Stir the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> through the curry and stir it all together for 1-2 min or until wilted – this is your <strong>sweetcorn chana curry</strong></p>",
