      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweetcorn chana curry </strong>over the <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice </strong>with the <strong>tomato & coriander salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Top with a dollop of <strong>mango chutney </strong>and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
